📚 Book Management Dashboard
A React + Vite dashboard for managing books. Supports full CRUD operations with modals, filters, pagination, and responsive UI using Tailwind CSS and Radix UI components.

🚀 Live Preview (Optional)
You can deploy this app to Vercel, Netlify, or GitHub Pages and add a live link here.

🔹 Features
📖 View list of books in a paginated grid/table

🔍 Search books by title or author

🎛️ Filter books by genre and status

➕ Add new books (with validation)

✏️ Edit existing books

🗑️ Delete books with confirmation popup

🔔 Toast notifications for success and errors

💅 Beautiful & responsive UI using Tailwind CSS and Radix UI

📦 Tech Stack
Layer	Technology
Frontend	
React 18
Build Tool - Vite
Forms:React Hook Form
UI Components: Radix UI
Styling: Tailwind CSS
Routing: React-Router-DOM
Animations:	Framer Motion
Icons:	Lucide React


